e line keep moving on, hungry faces, tired eyes"},{"s":101.28,"e":108.28,"text":"But when that prayer hits the room, even broken bones feel alive"},{"s":108.8,"e":114.62,"text":"Cause I been knocked down low, been counted out and left for dead"},{"s":114.62,"e":121.44,"text":"But the blessing on that food, turned my trouble into bread"},{"s":121.36,"e":127.42,"text":"St. John's plate, I'm fed, St. John's plate, I'm blessed"},{"s":127.34,"e":135.2,"text":"I still have a soul, and I still win like this"},{"s":135.12,"e":140.5,"text":"St. John's plate I ride, St. John's plate I live"},{"s":141.1,"e":148.84,"text":"They can't take my name, when I'm fed like this"},{"s":148.98,"e":155.28,"text":"If the world won't make room, I make room in my chest"},{"s":155.2,"e":162.02,"text":"For hope with a shaky hand, for grace in a plastic dish"},{"s":161.94,"e":168.22,"text":"And I don't need gold, I don't need a crown"},{"s":168.14,"e":175.04,"text":"I got that holy spoon, and I'm standing my ground"},{"s":174.96,"e":180.58,"text":"St. John's plate, I'm fed, St. John's plate, I'm blessed"},{"s":180.5,"e":188.48,"text":"I still have a soul, and I still win like this"},{"s":188.4,"e":193.86,"text":"St. John's plate I ride, St. John's plate I live"},{"s":194.22,"e":201.92,"text":"They can't take my name, when I'm fed like this"},{"s":204.96,"e":210.98,"text":"Fed like this, blessed like this"},{"s":211.22,"e":222.22,"text":"I still have a soul, I still win like this"}],"duration":233.48,"source":"whisper","generatedAt":"2026-06-01T00:00:00.000Z"}